    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists and friends just try to fix things that aren't even broken, they just want to keep the cycle going. but if you really look at it, if nothing actually has any objective meaning, then there's no real reason to keep pushing through the pain. it's just an endless loop for nothing.",
